{"tid":1897271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本或會停辦奧運 5月底將會有決定","createTime":"2020-02-25T15:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T16:25:46.000Z","uid":147376,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ab5d13284323b1c0ecc1f058ec3a83d9fe729f","tid":1897271,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20200225/s00006/1582619536643/【東京奧運】國際奧委會成員稱5月底定東奧命運-否定移師倫敦可行性\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20200225%2Fs00006%2F1582619536643%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E3%80%91%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%A5%A7%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B15%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%AE%9A%E6%9D%B1%E5%A5%A7%E5%91%BD%E9%81%8B-%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%9A%E7%A7%BB%E5%B8%AB%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWLvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=cfee6ff8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20200225%2Fs00006%2F1582619536643%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E3%80%91%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%A5%A7%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B15%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%AE%9A%E6%9D%B1%E5%A5%A7%E5%91%BD%E9%81%8B-%E5%90%A6%E5%AE%9A%E7%A7%BB%E5%B8%AB%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7&h=ebcf0545\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20200225/s00006/1582619536643/【東京奧運】國際奧委會成員稱5月底定東奧命運-否定移師倫敦可行性</a><br />\n東京奧運昨日步入150日倒數，希臘奧組委今日公布聖火採集詳情，惟新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情困擾下，賽事能否如期上演仍是未知數。國際奧委會成員Richard Pound透露，最快會於5月底決定賽事能否於7月展開。<br />\n<br />\n多項東京奧運資格賽受疫情影響延期或取消，義工培訓亦延遲展開，但賽會多次強調7月24日展開的奧運，100%不會延遲。國際奧委會資深成員Richard Pound接受美聯社訪問，透露會方將在5月底決定東京奧運的最終命運：「要在兩個月後，才能有決定，但很好準備工夫都在進行中。這是一個很大的決定（取消與否），需要很多可靠事實去支持，但現時收到的建議，取消或延期都不在考慮之列。」<br />\n正競逐倫敦市長的保守黨候選人貝利（Shaun Bailey），上周三表示倫敦可取代東京承辦今屆奧運，惟Richard Pound表示：「很難移師其他地方，當中牽涉太多設施，難在短期內完成建成。」<br />\n<br />\n儘管東奧前景未明，但聖火採集勢在必行。希臘奧組委今日公布詳情，聖火會於下月12日在奧運發源地希臘點燃，經8天傳遞後移師日本，在下月26日開始在日本國內傳遞。"},{"pid":"0fadec309ffbd2e79d38019d6922389c524c9f99","tid":1897271,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cce19d2bb51385d0e2a9c99593f5beb6da0c3c5","tid":1897271,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"輸幾千億<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3fa038f1627652832b5d7b3a546430676e64c4","tid":1897271,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cee155b52fdd6bf5f96870d317719d7771ae93ba","tid":1897271,"uid":53003,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"日本今次賠了夫人又折兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為面子死頂，結果自己控制唔到，又封鎖消息又盛，學晒偉大的中国一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9777a0594b59afb14691d65b6920b3415a1e70","tid":1897271,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"前日先講完唔會停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8444f2e7b05d9d0ada3ad15fc1f8a4002b123f","tid":1897271,"uid":224533,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"取消奧運，全球仇蚑情緒大爆發"},{"pid":"c6479906c426ab72aa3ba3667b234011c8b63389","tid":1897271,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"唔駛同遊客迫山手線<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信好多人會好高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923654aba38f4bc20a7ff789384929372ce8a409","tid":1897271,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"到5月日本人都死撚晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7